column5: Leaving Sunday September 6 for Gulllrock. Any new fishing reports out there? hot spots, depth you were catching them at, what was the hot bait. Thanks Bud

I just spent 4 hours on the lake this morning and we got fish , but not really big ones. The lake had a 3-4 foot chop on it so boat control was nonexistent. hiding behind round island we got them in 22 to 25 feet.there were some brave souls down by fishermans point and they were really bouncing around, there was also a couple of boats off the boot.
